title: Universal Understanding
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While on a [[plane]] with this property, a creature can understand the literal meaning of any spoken [[language]] that it hears and can understand any written language that it can see. This doesn't decode secret messages or reveal the meaning of symbols that aren't part of a written language.